  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink43-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">pāṉaṉ vāyilākap pukuntu teḷippa maṟutta talaimakaḷ pāṇaṉōṭu talaivaṉ
          pukuntu teḷittuḻic colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink43">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> ampaṇat taṉṉa yāmai yēṟic</l>
          <l> cempi ṉaṉṉa pārppuppala tuñcum</l>
          <l> yāṇa rūra niṉṉiṉum</l>
          <l> pāṇaṉ poyyaṉ palacū ḷiṉaṉē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> O man from the fertile village! </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> Where many young [tortoises] </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> clambering onto the [mother] tortoise's [back]</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> resembling a grain measure </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> sleep</l>
          <l rend="indent2"> resembling copper [bowls]</l>
          <l> </l>
          <l> Compared with you, [your bard] is the [better] liar, </l>
          <l> He who has made so many vows. </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
